        "subject": "LU-5326 libcfs: remove umode_t typedef",
        "message": "LU-5326 libcfs: remove umode_t typedef\n\nThe umode_t typedef in libcfs/include/libcfs/posix/posix-types.h is no\nlonger needed and causes lustre_user.h to be unusable outside of the\nlustre tree on powerpc64 so remove it.\n\nLustre-commit: dbe7a3219fc6fdaa8be7b3337a38964dcbb35f84\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/11055\n\nChange-Id: I0dc9c267a3aca7bbe07cfe7ad103b80f642c8b8f\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\n"
